{"total_count":5,"incomplete_results":false,"items":[{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/NousResearch/hermes-agent/commits/0cc63043e085dc6c12bc80007b6e6e3fafb7b3cf","sha":"0cc63043e085dc6c12bc80007b6e6e3fafb7b3cf","node_id":"MDY6Q29tbWl0MTAyNDU1NDI2NzowY2M2MzA0M2UwODVkYzZjMTJiYzgwMDA3YjZlNmUzZmFmYjdiM2Nm","html_url":"https://github.com/NousResearch/hermes-agent/commit/0cc63043e085dc6c12bc80007b6e6e3fafb7b3cf","comments_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/NousResearch/hermes-agent/commits/0cc63043e085dc6c12bc80007b6e6e3fafb7b3cf/comments","commit":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/NousResearch/hermes-agent/git/commits/0cc63043e085dc6c12bc80007b6e6e3fafb7b3cf","author":{"date":"2026-04-26T14:37:12.000+08:00","name":"阿泥豆","email":"1243352777@qq.com"},"committer":{"date":"2026-05-04T05:08:51.000-07:00","name":"Teknium","email":"127238744+teknium1@users.noreply.github.com"},"message":"fix(delegation): increase heartbeat stale thresholds\n\nThe heartbeat stale detection was too aggressive:\n- idle: 5 * 30s = 150s — LLM inference on slow providers (Zhipu/GLM)\n  frequently exceeds 150s, causing heartbeat to stop prematurely\n- in-tool: 20 * 30s = 600s — borderline for long tool calls\n\nWhen heartbeat stops, parent._last_activity_ts freezes, eventually\ntriggering gateway timeout and killing the entire delegation.\n\nNew thresholds:\n- idle: 15 * 30s = 450s — accommodates slow LLM inference\n- in-tool: 40 * 30s = 1200s — accommodates long-running tool calls\n\nchild_timeout_seconds (config: delegation.child_timeout_seconds) remains\nthe hard cap for total delegation duration.","tree":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/NousResearch/hermes-agent/git/trees/85002f5e82528058c8413c83820faf1d293a90e1","sha":"85002f5e82528058c8413c83820faf1d293a90e1"},"comment_count":0},"author":{"login":"zzy-git","id":20125584,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjIwMTI1NTg0","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/20125584?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/zzy-git","htm