te":"2026-04-22T11:20:16.000+08:00","name":"Kongxi","email":"vivien000812@gmail.com"},"committer":{"date":"2026-04-21T20:20:16.000-07:00","name":"GitHub","email":"noreply@github.com"},"message":"fix(delegation): add hard timeout and stale detection for subagent execution (#13770)\n\n- Wrap child.run_conversation() in a ThreadPoolExecutor with configurable\n  timeout (delegation.child_timeout_seconds, default 300s) to prevent\n  indefinite blocking when a subagent's API call or tool HTTP request hangs.\n\n- Add heartbeat stale detection: if a child's api_call_count doesn't\n  advance for 5 consecutive heartbeat cycles (~2.5 min), stop touching\n  the parent's activity timestamp so the gateway inactivity timeout\n  can fire as a last resort.\n\n- Add 'timeout' as a new exit_reason/status alongside the existing\n  completed/max_iterations/interrupted states.\n\n- Use shutdown(wait=False) on the timeout executor to avoid the\n  ThreadPoolExecutor.__exit__ deadlock when a child is stuck on\n  blocking I/O.\n\nCloses #13768","tree":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/NousResearch/hermes-agent/git/trees/25c973ab16ae8eff916c7e004773bc176a3ad759","sha":"25c973ab16ae8eff916c7e004773bc176a3ad759"},"comment_count":0},"author":{"login":"iamagenius00","id":275581506,"node_id":"U_kgDOEG0KQg","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/275581506?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/iamagenius00","html_url":"https://github.com/iamagenius00","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/iamagenius00/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/iamagenius00/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/iamagenius00/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/iamagenius00/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/iamagenius00/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/iamagenius00/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/iamagenius00/repos","even